ic background for a wider range of particle masses and\ncross-sections.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Jul 2005 15:51:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 2 May 2006 19:07:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
