ega|$ and an anomalous damping of spin waves proportional to\n$nf^4|\\omega|$ are obtained.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Jul 2005 08:11:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 17 Nov 2005 09:31:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
